see RiskTx.org 

Master now switched to Scala 2.8.0, Lift 2.1 and Akka 0.10


Install Java SDK
Install git
Install sbt from http://code.google.com/p/simple-build-tool/
Install mongodb from http://www.mongodb.org/
Fork this repository and clone it
run:
 sbt update
 sbt jetty

Open a browser and go to http://localhost:8080/
